{{Infobox Union |name= EL & IT |country= [[Norway]] |affiliation= [[Norwegian Confederation of Trade Unions|LO]] |members= 37,000 |full_name= EL & IT Forbundet |native_name= |image= [[Image:EL&IT logo.png|200px]] |founded= 1999 |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= [[Oslo]], Norway |people= [[Jan Olav Andersen]], president |website= [http://www.elogit.no www.elogit.no] |footnotes= }} <!-- Include all unused fields for future use. See [[template talk:Infobox Union]] for usage. -->
'''EL & IT Forbundet''' is a [[trade union]] in [[Norway]]. It was formed by the 1999 merger of the [[Electricians and Power Station Workers]], and the [[Data and Telecommunications Workers]].
EL & IT Forbundet has a membership of over 37,000 and is affiliated with the [[Norwegian Confederation of Trade Unions]] (LO).
[[Hans O. Felix]] was president of the union from 2001 to 2015. [[Jan Olav Andersen]] was elected in March 2015.<!-- Norwegian language source: http://frifagbevegelse.no/nettverk/felix_tar_ikke_gjenvalg_305686.html http://frifagbevegelse.no/arbeidsliv/el__it_forbundet_valgte_jan_olav_andersen_som_ny_forbundsleder_328262.html -->
