{{Greek Basket League awards}} [[File:Νίκος Γκάλης.jpg|thumb|upright|240px|[[Nikos Galis]] was the [[Greek Basket League]] Finals MVP 5 times (1987, 1988, 1989, 1990, 1991).]] The '''Greek Basket League Finals MVP''', or '''Greek Basket League Playoffs MVP''' [[Greek Basket League awards|award]] ([[Greek language|Greek]]: Ελληνικού Α1 Μπάσκετ Πρωταθλήματος Tελικός MVP) is the yearly Finals MVP award for the playoff finals of the [[Greek basketball league system|1st-tier]] professional [[basketball]] league in [[Greece]], the [[Greek Basket League]].
